metadata.name: Scarborough Fair
metadata.description:
"If you need to learn how to talk to a lady, ask your mum."

The theme for this piece is the Break Dance of the Witch. An audacious technique where the witch twirls around on her back while firing off numerous bullets using her four hand and feet gun weapons: Parsley, Sage, Rosemary and Thyme.


ᴘʀɪᴠᴀᴛᴇ ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇɴᴛ sᴇʀᴠɪᴄᴇ
